  "detailed_description": "<h1>NEWS</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our new game is coming soon! 🎮 Add it to your wishlist now! ✨ SILICONE HEART<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549580/extras/5dabde5ff942057c7c2c11fb537fe868.poster.avif?t=1770751224\" width=800 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549580/extras/5dabde5ff942057c7c2c11fb537fe868.webm?t=1770751224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549580/extras/5dabde5ff942057c7c2c11fb537fe868.mp4?t=1770751224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Only Up!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549580/extras/518743e8d3f7d7a8bcc29b93cda386af.poster.avif?t=1770751224\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549580/extras/518743e8d3f7d7a8bcc29b93cda386af.webm?t=1770751224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549580/extras/518743e8d3f7d7a8bcc29b93cda386af.mp4?t=1770751224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Step into a challenge where your primary goal is to jump high and climb fast to escape the rising lava beneath your feet. Give no chances to either the lava or your competitors - always move up!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >100-player Multiplayer!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549580/extras/fc27b73dc4712ab63d2e1cec56ca69f1.poster.avif?t=1770751224\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549580/extras/fc27b73dc4712ab63d2e1cec56ca69f1.webm?t=1770751224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549580/extras/fc27b73dc4712ab63d2e1cec56ca69f1.mp4?t=1770751224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Fight, push, knock down, and set cunning traps to be the last player on the path to the top. Every competitor is ready to play dirty for victory. Always stay one step ahead!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Floor is Lava!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549580/extras/7dde88446b8b9cb1af834ed7665879f1.poster.avif?t=1770751224\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549580/extras/7dde88446b8b9cb1af834ed7665879f1.webm?t=1770751224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549580/extras/7dde88446b8b9cb1af834ed7665879f1.mp4?t=1770751224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The lava relentlessly rises, making every pause a potential danger. You'll need to run faster, think strategically, and constantly move forward and up to survive.<br><br>Beware! Every step you take can be decisive. The unpredictability of the game and the competition with other players demands your full focus and lightning-fast reflexes. Don't let yourself be caught by opponents or the raging lava!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Various Game Modes</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549580/extras/983d52e322872a10d199fe1f924c5ede.poster.avif?t=1770751224\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549580/extras/983d52e322872a10d199fe1f924c5ede.webm?t=1770751224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549580/extras/983d52e322872a10d199fe1f924c5ede.mp4?t=1770751224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Try out different modes, from fast matches with disappearing platforms under your feet to classic runs reminiscent of squid games, where every second counts.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Parkour and Extreme</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549580/extras/b77660ced647b6e11a5ecffe2a003ad5.poster.avif?t=1770751224\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549580/extras/b77660ced647b6e11a5ecffe2a003ad5.webm?t=1770751224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2549580/extras/b77660ced647b6e11a5ecffe2a003ad5.mp4?t=1770751224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Master game mechanics, perform risky jumps through unexpected traps, and adapt to a constantly changing track. Excellent skill mastery and quick reflexes are required for a successful run.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Private Servers</h2>Create your own server with friends and enjoy the game in a cozy group, independent of the rest of the world.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Constant Updates!</h2>We're always on the move! The more you play, the faster we release new features. Expect regular updates, including cosmetic enhancements, new modes, and many other functions.",
